The Standing Committee on Public Accounts (Scopa) will tomorrow hold a hearing with the South African Airways (SAA) on their annual report, financial statements, irregular, fruitless and wasteful expenditure for the 2016/17 financial year.  Details of the meeting: Date:               Tuesday, 24 April 2018
Time:               10:00
Venue:              E249, 2nd floor, New Wing Building Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Republic of South Africa: The Parliament.